highlights.text: “FIRST LOVE” by Oscar Ortiz and Edgardo Nuñez is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 64 spots at #129.
Drake has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Rich Baby Daddy (feat. Sexyy Red & SZA)” is the highest at #19.
“HISS” by Megan Thee Stallion is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #3.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 193 weeks straight.
